The first authoritative guide to optimizing your PC&amp;#039;s BIOS

Your PC&amp;#039;s BIOS enables your software and hardware to work together. But they can work together betterÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â‚¬ï¿½way better. If you want the best possible PC performance and stability, this book shows you exactly what to tweak, and how to tweak it.

